                <div class="col-lg-8 pt-4 pt-lg-0 content" data-aos="fade-left">
              <h3>Entry Level Full Stack Web Designer</h3>
                 <p class="fst-italic">
                    Hello! My name is Brittany Dodd. I absolutely love designing, customizing, problem solving, and facing 
                    new challenges. I have had a passion for computers that I shared with my dad growing up. Becoming a <strong>Full Stack Web
                    Developer</strong> is the best way for me to be able to do all of these things in a career field I can grow in. 
                 </p>
                <div class="col-lg-9 offset-3" data-aos="fade-right">
                   <img id= "DadAndI"src="assets/img/MyPhotos/DadNoFrame.png" class="img-fluid" alt="">   
                   <p>
                        My dad was a computer science major in college when I was a young kid. Growing up, being surrounded by computers on a daily basis, 
                        whether he was building them, fixing them, or just having fun on them, it was a way of life in our household. After having kiddos of my own, 
                        I realized I wanted to follow in my dads footsteps and start my career in the Web Developer world.
                   </p>
                 </div>
                </div>
        </div>
    </div><!-- End About Me -->


